  <brief_title>Patient Satisfaction With Propofol for Out Patient Colonoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Patient Satisfaction With Propofol for Out Patient Colonoscopy: A Prospective, Randomized, Double-Blind Study</official_title>
